{
  "stem": "2851.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know where we walk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we walked to see people, to see a city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These people?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They live in Israel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Her name was Gittel and Tova.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And her brother was Avrum.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we walk together until we came to Maniewicze.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there we-- we find one man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was Jewish, so we ask him, where is a place to live?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There is some Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, go in into this house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a lady.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She will-- she will give you a place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she will give you eat-- something to eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when I came in, I saw my-- my mother's cousin-- my mother's cousin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name is Faigy-- [NON-ENGLISH] Faigy, yeah-- her-- the same name like my mother-- Sadler-- Faigy Sadler.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she didn't let us go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She gave us bread and everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we-- we start to live.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I was-- we been crying-- both of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She start to cry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was very happy to see us-- me and my sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she took us all in her house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We slept over a few nights.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she gave us bread and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we-- we've been looking for another place to live.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We find a place.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we live all together-- the two sisters, and the brother, and me and my sister.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maniewicze.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We find a house, a empty house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No one help us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I washed the-- the-- from the-- from the Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I washed their-- their clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then-- and then it was very hard for me to do that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, when we had a place-- so one-- so-- so one woman said she has a machine-- a thing-- a sewing machine.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
